document_data.mainbody:
Aithe High Street was a the main road that passed through Aithelar in Callidyrr on the Moonshae Isles in .
Aithe High Street passed through the center of town, running north to south. It intersected many of Aithelars other streets including Bottle Lane, Whitefish Alley, Eel Street, Rope End Lane, Finns Alley, Aerynns Street, Blackdorns Way and Blaedar Street.
